  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个DNA数据存储文件格式的整体架构。核心是一个根节点，下面分五大块：头部信息、数据区、压缩区、纠错区，还有一个区块链注册区。这个结构能覆盖从原始数据到链上存证的全流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNA Data Storage File Format",
        "Header Section",
        "Data Section",
        "Compression Section",
        "Error Correction Section",
        "Blockchain Enrollment Section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，根节点用圆角矩形表示DNA数据存储文件格式。我确认一下头部信息的具体字段：格式版本、元数据、原始数据哈希，还有压缩算法和纠错算法的标识，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Header Section",
        "Format Version",
        "Metadata",
        "Original Data Hash",
        "Compression Algorithm",
        "Error Correction Algorithm"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，头部这五个字段缺一不可。数据区放分块后的原始数据，压缩区和纠错区分别存储处理后的结果。区块链注册区比较特殊，需要包含工作量证明。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Header Section",
        "Chunked Data",
        "Compression Section",
        "Error Correction Section",
        "Blockchain Enrollment Section",
        "Proof-of-Work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把五大区块都挂到根节点下了。数据区下面放了分块数据，压缩区下面挂了压缩后的数据，纠错区对应纠错数据，区块链区放了工作量证明节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Section",
        "Chunked Data",
        "Compression Section",
        "Compressed Data",
        "Error Correction Section",
        "Error Correction Data",
        "Blockchain Enrollment Section",
        "Proof-of-Work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，压缩区的命名需要调整一下。我们实际存储的是压缩后的数据，不是压缩这个动作。另外头部里的压缩算法字段只是标识用了什么算法，要和压缩区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Compression Section",
        "Compressed Data",
        "Compression Algorithm",
        "Header Section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下：压缩算法保留在头部作为元数据字段，压缩区下面明确标注为压缩数据。这样层次就清晰了，算法标识在头，实际压缩结果在独立区块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Compression Algorithm",
        "Header Section",
        "Compression Section",
        "Compressed Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在结构对了。再确认一遍根节点的五个分支：头部信息、数据区、压缩区、纠错区、区块链注册区。每个区块的职责没有重叠，读取时按顺序解析即可。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNA Data Storage File Format",
        "Header Section",
        "Data Section",
        "Compression Section",
        "Error Correction Section",
        "Blockchain Enrollment Section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
